excerpt: Mindvalley Labs Sdn. Bhd. is a company based in Malaysia, with its head office in Kuala Lumpur. It operates in the Electronics Stores sector. The company was established on January 10, 2005. In its most recent financial highlights, the company reported a net sales revenue increase of 3.52% in 2021. Its total assets grew by 19.2% over the same period. The net profit margin of Mindvalley Labs Sdn. Bhd. increased by 0.13% in 2021.
title: Mindvalley Labs Sdn. Bhd. (Malaysia)
